                The <b>Eastern New York Soccer Referee Association (ENYSRA)</b>
                provides referees for the Eastern New York State Soccer Association (ENYSSA)
                and Eastern New York Youth Soccer Association (ENYYSA). Our referees are certified
                through the USSF and are part of the ENYSRA Eastern New York Soccer Referee Association.
                <br /><br />
                We welcome new and experienced referees to join us,
                and simply ask that you be committed to working on a regular and consistent basis
                throughout each soccer season to develop, improve, and refine your officiating skills,
                and that you honor your commitments for game assignments.
